 />\n資料來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_pubsvc/page_offdr/sub_communityb/id_csoscheme/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Findex%2Fsite_pubsvc%2Fpage_offdr%2Fsub_communityb%2Fid_csoscheme%2F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97SUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=11bc1a46\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_pubsvc/page_offdr/sub_communityb/id_csoscheme/</a><br />\n<br />\n睇返資料同法例<br />\n幾時做，做啲乜，做幾耐由督導感化主任指示<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果區諾軒本身無業咁的確可安排佢全天候日日8小時去做社會服務令ge，咁<br />\n就咁睇，個督導感化主任唔妥條友，以安排到啲野好閪都得<br />\n<br />\n同埋有無完成都一定有記錄，有做到唔怕ge<br />\n<br />\n我出左呢個回覆會唔會被人當5毛畜牲嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af54664d9402b3afe59499c5fb42c431b837c744","tid":2458054,"uid":5489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb6e9708da15e471c316ed4efdb73053cac6c513","tid":2458054,"uid":266010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d49aa28bbd3b1563a4769c59eee359fc0f76fd5d","tid":2458054,"uid":81345,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"b2f532db4ec8c386bde857f8a1c489fd95b97ec4","tid":2458054,"uid":266010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20d488e3f07d9860900623f677d3f90caceeb63f","tid":2458054,"uid":81345,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:10:55.000Z","msg":"我記得唔係你想做就做<br />\n係監你嗰條友叫你做就做<br />\n想做幾多，做啲乜，做幾耐都無得自己揀<br />\n只能接受無得拒絕<br />\n<br />\n我以前有聽過係咁<br />\n所以啲人對監佢嗰個烚熟狗頭咁<br />\n有錯請指正"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:36:26.000Z","msg":"簡 介<br />\n社 會 服 務 令 計 劃 是 一 項 根 據 香 港 法 例 第 378 章 &lt;&lt; 社 會 服 務 令 條 例&gt;&gt; 的 社 區 層 面 的 判 