2Fid_csoscheme%2F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97SUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=11bc1a46\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.swd.gov.hk/tc/index/site_pubsvc/page_offdr/sub_communityb/id_csoscheme/</a><br />\n<br />\n睇返資料同法例<br />\n幾時做，做啲乜，做幾耐由督導感化主任指示<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果區諾軒本身無業咁的確可安排佢全天候日日8小時去做社會服務令ge，咁<br />\n就咁睇，個督導感化主任唔妥條友，以安排到啲野好閪都得<br />\n<br />\n同埋有無完成都一定有記錄，有做到唔怕ge<br />\n<br />\n我出左呢個回覆會唔會被人當5毛畜牲嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T01:19:52.000Z","msg":"會，連登仔就是想自己都呃埋賺取打飛機快感，阻人自high會俾人燒春袋架。<br />\n<br />\n個感化官唔安排既野做左唔算架。"},{"pid":"879952788ba63ac8a82b728e3aaea00f4e5f73cf","tid":2458054,"uid":21113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T01:24:29.000Z","msg":"而家仲疫佢老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80be45813d4131e673c3741ce9356b5fc129a40b","tid":2458054,"uid":2020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af54664d9402b3afe59499c5fb42c431b837c744","tid":2458054,"uid":5489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T01:25:18.000Z","msg":"佢單野好耐喇 上年年中已經判左"},{"pid":"186ee320b4e3098b3567151123828e13ad8a05a1","tid":2458054,"uid":81345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80be45813d4131e673c3741ce9356b5fc129a40b","tid":2458054,"uid":2020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af54664d9402b3afe59499c5fb42c431b837c744","tid":2458054,"uid":5489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T11:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T01:25:18.000Z","msg":"佢單野好耐喇 上年年中已經判左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T01:26:31.000Z","msg":"如果係咁，100個鐘半年差唔多啦<br